===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|すね|alt=臑,腨,脚,髄}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|すね|tr=sune|t=[[marrow]]|sort=すね}}; appears in the ''{{w|Kojiki}}'' (712) in the name of a deity: {{lang|ja|登美能那賀'''須泥'''毘古}} (''to₂mi₁-no₂-naga-'''sune'''-bi₁ko₁''), whose name is also attested logographically in the ''{{w|Nihon Shoki}}'' (720) as {{lang|ja|長'''髄'''彦}}.<ref name="JDBsune">{{R:JDB|page=390}}</ref><ref name="KDJ2Osune"/>

====Pronunciation====
{{ja-pron|すね|acc=2|acc_ref=<ref name="KDJ2Osune">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2 Online|すね 【脛・臑・腨・脚・髄】|lid=2002024d5c22638fZrkj|kotobank=脛-542840#w-2017421}}</ref>,DJR,NHK}}
